Career Options


Today, Idea is a formidable player in the telecom business with unparalleled energy, passion and creativity unleashed by the talent pool within. Idea’s journey to what it is today has been a story in itself, a unique and uncommon one in many aspects! 
As an organization we look for professionals who are :
Self Driven
Innovative
Analytical
Team Players
 
We have wide array of opportunities for fresher as well as laterals. 




YOUNG LEADERS
Our Management Trainee program, christened Idea Young Leaders' Program has been designed to provide young leaders an accelerated path to reach their career goals. Every year we visit Premier B-schools, Engineering colleges & CA Institute at corporate level for hiring the best talent for roles at the junior management level.
The Program

                         On joining, the YL's go through a one-year rigorous trainee program.
This program offers challenging work assignments complemented by a learning component.
This combination of practical work experience, formal training, and support by career development mentors provides participants with a unique opportunity to develop and assume challenging responsibilities within the organization.




Experienced Professionals
We also provide a wide array of career opportunity across various functions for the experienced professionals.
Key roles for which we typically look to hire professional are:

Sales – Zonal Business Managers, Area Sales Managers, Key Account Managers, Distribution Managers
Marketing – Telecom Product Management ( Voice, VAS, Mobile Broadband), Brand Management
Finance – Business Planning, Revenue Assurance, Financial Accounting
Network Services – Operations and Maintenance, Network Planning
Service Delivery – Customer Life cycle Operations, Contact Centre Management









